---
title: BeaconLink Deployment State Machine
---

stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deployment Creation
    %% =====================================================

    [*] --> Created

    Created : Deployment Requested
    Created : Immutable Revision Created
    Created : Metadata Recorded

    Created --> Validating

    %% =====================================================
    %% Validation Phase
    %% =====================================================

    Validating : Validate Manifest
    Validating : Validate Schema
    Validating : Validate Dependencies

    Validating --> PolicyEvaluation : Validation Passed
    Validating --> Failed : Validation Failed

    PolicyEvaluation : RBAC Verification
    PolicyEvaluation : Compliance Checks
    PolicyEvaluation : Placement Policies

    PolicyEvaluation --> Planning : Authorized
    PolicyEvaluation --> Rejected : Policy Denied

    Rejected : Deployment Rejected
    Rejected : Await User Action

    Rejected --> [*]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Planning Phase
    %% =====================================================

    Planning : Build Execution Plan
    Planning : Resolve Dependencies
    Planning : Determine Execution Graph

    Planning --> Scheduling

    Scheduling : Capability-Based Scheduling
    Scheduling : Select Target Agents
    Scheduling : Reserve Capacity

    Scheduling --> Dispatching : Targets Selected
    Scheduling --> Waiting : Capacity Unavailable

    Waiting : Await Available Capacity
    Waiting --> Scheduling : Resources Available
    Waiting --> Cancelled : Cancel Requested

    %% =====================================================
    %% Dispatch Phase
    %% =====================================================

    Dispatching : Deliver Desired State
    Dispatching : Send Immutable Revision

    Dispatching --> Executing

    %% =====================================================
    %% Runtime Execution
    %% =====================================================

    state Executing {

        [*] --> Preparing

        Preparing : Resolve Secrets
        Preparing : Download Artifacts
        Preparing : Verify Runtime

        Preparing --> Applying

        Applying : Apply Desired State
        Applying : Runtime Translation
        Applying : Resource Creation

        Applying --> Verifying

        Verifying : Health Checks
        Verifying : Readiness Checks
        Verifying : State Validation

        Verifying --> Running : Deployment Healthy
        Verifying --> Retrying : Recoverable Failure
        Verifying --> Rollback : Verification Failed

        Retrying : Retry Deployment

        Retrying --> Applying
        Retrying --> Rollback : Retry Limit Exceeded

        Rollback : Restore Previous Revision

        Rollback --> Failed : Rollback Failed
        Rollback --> RolledBack : Rollback Successful

        Running : Desired State Achieved

        Running --> [*]

    }

    %% =====================================================
    %% Successful Deployment
    %% =====================================================

    Executing --> Completed

    Completed : Deployment Successful
    Completed : Inventory Updated
    Completed : Events Published

    Completed --> Monitoring

    %% =====================================================
    %% Continuous Operation
    %% =====================================================

    Monitoring : Continuous Reconciliation
    Monitoring : Drift Detection
    Monitoring : Health Monitoring

    Monitoring --> Reconciling : Drift Detected
    Monitoring --> Scaling : Scaling Requested
    Monitoring --> Updating : New Revision
    Monitoring --> Deleting : Delete Requested

    Reconciling : Restore Desired State

    Reconciling --> Monitoring

    Scaling : Scale Workload

    Scaling --> Monitoring

    Updating : Deploy New Revision

    Updating --> Dispatching

    %% =====================================================
    %% Deletion Lifecycle
    %% =====================================================

    Deleting : Graceful Termination
    Deleting : Remove Resources

    Deleting --> Deleted

    Deleted : Deployment Removed

    Deleted --> [*]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Failure States
    %% =====================================================

    RolledBack : Previous Revision Active

    RolledBack --> Monitoring
    RolledBack --> Updating : New Revision

    Failed : Deployment Failed
    Failed : Await Operator Action

    Failed --> Rollback
    Failed --> Updating
    Failed --> Cancelled

    Cancelled : Deployment Cancelled

    Cancelled --> [*]

    %% =====================================================
    %% Global Transitions
    %% =====================================================

    Monitoring --> Failed : Runtime Failure
    Executing --> Failed : Critical Error
    Dispatching --> Failed : Communication Failure
    Scheduling --> Failed : Scheduler Failure